'''Buuraha Jawlaan''' ([[Carabi]] هضبة الجولان) waa dhul banaan oo ku yaal waqooyi bari Israa'iil oo ay Israa'iil ka qabsatay Suuriya dagaalkii lixda maalmood ee 1967.<ref>[http://www.britannica.com/EBchecked/topic/237237/Golan-Heights Golan Heights], Britannica.</ref> [[Qaramada Midoobay]] ayaa u codaysay inay Israa'iil weydiisato inay ciidamadeeda kala baxdo Buuraha Jawlaan.<ref>[http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-middle-east-14724842 bbc.co.uk.]</ref> Suuriya iyo Israa'iil weli ma saxeexin heshiis nabadeed oo ka yimid dagaalkaas, badiba arrinta Golan awgeed. Waxa ay ku sigteen in ay heshiis nabadeed gaaraan, balse waxa ay ku heshiin waayeen halka laga soo saarayo, iyo waxa ay tahay in Suuriya ay soo celiso.<ref>https://web.archive.org/web/20101008052046/http://www.un.int/syria/golan.htm ([http://www.un.int/syria/golan.htm eeg asalka])</ref> Buuraha Jawlaan iyo Buur Hermon waxaa la wareegay Israa'iil 1981. Dhinaca galbeed ee Buuraha Jawlaan waxa ku yaal folkaano  hurday oo dabar go’ay.
